title: Victorious Maokai
body:
Just wondering why I have received all of my rewards except for the Victorious Maokai skin, please let me know what I need to do to receive the skin and if anyone else is having this issue. 

Thanks

replies.body: The goal is for the 21st, but most accounts are actually done receiving their rewards.  We're not entirely finished though, because some players still have some content missing like victorious skins.  It's on the way, so don't worry and hold tight.  The goodies will be arriving!
It's normal to not get all of the rewards at the same time. They are still being given out, so just be patient and you will get the skin soon enough. The goal is to get everything out by the 21st.
